We must forge and/or strengthen collaborations between patients, community members, other key stakeholders, healthcare providers, healthcare institutions, professional societies, and legislative bodies. Herein, we provide a high-level review of current disparities in chronic liver disease and describe actionable strategies which have potential to bridge gaps, improve quality and promote equity in liver care.
